span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 23, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ids1665703544688.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ids1665703544688.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ids1665703544688.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ids1665703544688\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ids1665703544688__access_key_1667\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A character in a widget label or menu item that when pressed, often in combination with <span class=\"ph keypress\">Alt</span>, gives focus to, or activates, the widget or menu item.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ids1665703544688__p_d14e1_d15e1_d16e1\">Synonyms: hot key</p>\n<p class=\"p\">A key or combination of keys that, when pressed, gives focus to or activates a widget. Most\n      access keys involve holding down an extra key, such as Alt , while pressing an alphabetic key,\n      for example, Alt+E.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ids1665703544688__p_d17e1_d18e1_d19e1\">Access keys are defined within Uniface, but are processed by the\n      GUI, if supported.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ids1665703544688__p_d20e1_d21e1_d22e1\">Valid alphabetic keys are indicated by mnemonics on the current form, which are highlighted or underlined, depending on the platform used. The Enter and Escape keys are also access keys. In some circumstances (for example, when choosing an item from a menu) the use of the modifier key is not required.</p>\n</div>\n\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tjd1665703544759.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>menu</a><p>A type of global object that enables users to see and execute application commands in a desktop application. A menu can be displayed as a menu bar, a drop-down menu (in a menu bar or cascaded menu), or a pop-up menu.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/awj1665703544619.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>accelerator</a><p>A keystroke or combination of keystrokes that performs an action, such as Ctrl+O to open a file.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528500\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528500\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "access key Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 23, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 A character in a widget label or menu item that when pressed, often in combination with Alt , gives focus to, or activates, the widget or menu item. Synonyms: hot key A key or combination of keys that, when pressed, gives focus to or activates a widget. Most access keys involve holding down an extra key, such as Alt , while pressing an alphabetic key, for example, Alt+E. Access keys are defined within Uniface, but are processed by the GUI, if supported. Valid alphabetic keys are indicated by mnemonics on the current form, which are highlighted or underlined, depending on the platform used. The Enter and Escape keys are also access keys. In some circumstances (for example, when choosing an item from a menu) the use of the modifier key is not required. Related Links menu A type of global object that enables users to see and execute application commands in a desktop application. A menu can be displayed as a menu bar, a drop-down menu (in a menu bar or cascaded menu), or a pop-up menu. accelerator A keystroke or combination of keystrokes that performs an action, such as Ctrl+O to open a file. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}